18
00:00:12,582 --> 00:00:15,582
http://hiqve.com/

19
00:00:18,606 --> 00:00:19,732
<i>invasion!</i>

20
00:00:19,899 --> 00:00:22,985
<i>The planet Cato Neimoidia
is under Separatist attack!</i>

21
00:00:23,361 --> 00:00:26,197
<i>Anakin Skywalker
and his Padawan, Ahsoka Tano,</i>

22
00:00:26,322 --> 00:00:27,448
<i>rush to the rescue</i>

23
00:00:27,490 --> 00:00:31,285
<i>as they lead a squadron of star fighters
to the planet below.</i>

24
00:00:39,210 --> 00:00:41,337
Ahsoka, punch a hole
for the gunships to get through.

25
00:00:41,879 --> 00:00:43,506
I know the drill, Master.

26
00:01:07,363 --> 00:01:08,906
Look out! Incoming missiles!

27
00:01:11,742 --> 00:01:12,868
No problem.

28
00:01:16,247 --> 00:01:17,873
Uh, slight problem.

29
00:01:20,585 --> 00:01:23,254
Ahsoka, I've got buzz droids.
How bad did you get hit?

30
00:01:23,337 --> 00:01:24,589
I'm all clear.

31
00:01:24,714 --> 00:01:27,592
What? You always have it easy, Snips.

32
00:01:34,557 --> 00:01:35,891
Good job, Artoo.

33
00:01:37,143 --> 00:01:40,563
Someday, these droids will learn
they keep messing with the wrong Jedi.

34
00:01:41,897 --> 00:01:43,274
Looks like you're clear.

35
00:01:43,357 --> 00:01:45,901
Just keep watching and learning, Padawan.

36
00:01:47,612 --> 00:01:48,988
Uh-oh.

37
00:01:49,071 --> 00:01:51,073
You're trailing smoke. What's wrong?

38
00:01:51,198 --> 00:01:54,869
Oh, nothing serious,
just a small malfunction.

39
00:01:59,332 --> 00:02:01,584
Master? Master, come in.

40
00:02:01,709 --> 00:02:04,503
<i>Artoo, what's going on over there?</i>

41
00:02:05,671 --> 00:02:08,382
Unconscious? Fly back to the cruiser.

42
00:02:09,925 --> 00:02:12,178
What do you mean there is something
wrong with the engines?

43
00:02:12,261 --> 00:02:14,096
Tip your wing. I'll see how bad it is.

44
00:02:18,392 --> 00:02:20,019
Oh, that's not good.

45
00:02:21,604 --> 00:02:23,939
Let's just say
now would be a good time to land.

46
00:02:26,609 --> 00:02:29,153
Artoo, can you land the ship
on that cliff ledge?

47
00:02:30,863 --> 00:02:33,949
I don't care if the landing zone is too short.

48
00:02:34,033 --> 00:02:35,618
Get that ship on the ground!

49
00:02:37,078 --> 00:02:41,415
R7, take over the ship.
I'm going after Anakin.

50
00:02:42,041 --> 00:02:44,085
Somebody has to save his skin.

51
00:03:22,957 --> 00:03:24,041
Artoo!

52
00:03:32,633 --> 00:03:34,844
Very funny, Artoo.

53
00:03:34,927 --> 00:03:37,304
Are you okay, Master?

54
00:03:37,388 --> 00:03:39,974
Yeah, what'd I miss?

55
00:03:40,182 --> 00:03:42,601
Oh, not much.

56
00:03:42,685 --> 00:03:45,521
Wait a minute, wasn't I flying?
Where's my fighter?

57
00:03:45,604 --> 00:03:46,689
How did I get here?

58
00:03:46,772 --> 00:03:49,316
Fighter crashed. I saved the day.
You're welcome.

59
00:03:54,155 --> 00:03:55,239
All right.

60
00:03:57,992 --> 00:04:00,745
Captain Rex,
Ahsoka and I need a little help.

61
00:04:00,828 --> 00:04:01,996
Right away, sir.

62
00:04:11,589 --> 00:04:12,673
Master Yoda...

63
00:04:12,757 --> 00:04:16,010
<i>Return to the Jedi Temple quickly,
you should.</i>

64
00:04:16,093 --> 00:04:17,303
<i>You and your Padawan.</i>

65
00:04:17,386 --> 00:04:19,805
We're kind of busy, Master Yoda.

66
00:04:19,889 --> 00:04:23,684
<i>The reason we need you,
important it is, Skywalker.</i>

67
00:04:23,768 --> 00:04:26,395
<i>Bombed the Temple hangar someone has.</i>

68
00:04:26,479 --> 00:04:29,231
<i>Your assistance to
find the terrorist, we need.</i>

69
00:04:29,356 --> 00:04:32,276
Who could successfully bomb
the Jedi Temple?

70
00:04:32,359 --> 00:04:34,570
We'll be right there, Master.

71
00:04:45,998 --> 00:04:48,292
How could the Separatists
infiltrate the Temple?

72
00:04:48,751 --> 00:04:50,836
Worse than that, it is.

73
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:53,214
What could be worse, Master Yoda?

74
00:04:57,593 --> 00:04:59,386
Everything is on the table.

75
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:00,930
We have to look at the possibility

76
00:05:01,013 --> 00:05:04,600
that it could've been anyone
in the Temple, even a Jedi.

77
00:05:04,683 --> 00:05:09,563
If a Jedi this is,
gone to the dark side they have.

78
00:05:09,939 --> 00:05:15,069
I can't believe a Jedi
would attack a place this sacred.

79
00:05:15,694 --> 00:05:18,280
We'd like for you two
to lead the investigation.

80
00:05:18,405 --> 00:05:20,282
We can't trust anyone who was here,

81
00:05:20,366 --> 00:05:21,617
even a Jedi.

82
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:24,203
You and Ahsoka will provide
an impartial point of view,

83
00:05:24,286 --> 00:05:25,371
free of assumptions.

84
00:05:25,454 --> 00:05:27,206
We'll do everything we can.

85
00:05:27,289 --> 00:05:30,251
Careful you must be, Skywalker.

86
00:05:30,334 --> 00:05:33,254
If willing to destroy the Temple
the attacker is,

87
00:05:33,337 --> 00:05:36,382
to great lengths they will go
to keep from being caught.

88
00:05:36,799 --> 00:05:41,095
Then I guess we'll have to go
to even greater lengths to catch him.

89
00:05:48,477 --> 00:05:50,479
I can still hear the screams.

90
00:05:50,563 --> 00:05:52,481
Do you believe what they said, Master?

91
00:05:52,565 --> 00:05:54,275
That a Jedi could do this?

92
00:05:54,358 --> 00:05:57,611
Not every Jedi
agrees with this war, Ahsoka.

93
00:05:57,695 --> 00:06:00,197
There are many
political idealists among us.

94
00:06:00,281 --> 00:06:01,949
But a traitor?

95
00:06:02,032 --> 00:06:05,119
I'm afraid one
can eventually become the other.

96
00:06:05,202 --> 00:06:09,540
Remember Count Dooku and General Krell,
that's how they started, too.

97
00:06:09,623 --> 00:06:13,711
Only analysis and investigation
will prove what is true or not.

98
00:06:14,461 --> 00:06:15,713
Who are you?

99
00:06:15,796 --> 00:06:19,967
I am Russo-ISC,
Crime Scene Analyzer for the Jedi.

100
00:06:20,467 --> 00:06:22,803
I will be working with you
and your Padawan on this case.

101
00:06:24,138 --> 00:06:26,807
I was assigned by Master Windu.

102
00:06:27,725 --> 00:06:30,936
Okay, Russo. You and Ahsoka
should begin the interviews.

103
00:06:31,145 --> 00:06:34,815
I would rather interview
the witnesses alone.

104
00:06:36,859 --> 00:06:37,902
Why?

105
00:06:37,985 --> 00:06:42,114
Many of the wounded have heard rumors
a Jedi was behind this explosion.

106
00:06:42,781 --> 00:06:45,910
There will be ill-will toward you.

107
00:06:47,494 --> 00:06:49,496
I think you're over-exaggerating, Russo.

108
00:06:49,580 --> 00:06:53,542
There were Jedi killed in that blast
along with maintenance crew and clones.

109
00:06:53,667 --> 00:06:54,919
Take Ahsoka with you.

110
00:06:55,502 --> 00:06:57,338
Let me know if you find anything.

111
00:06:57,463 --> 00:06:58,797
I will, Master.

112
00:07:10,684 --> 00:07:14,355
Did you notice
anything unusual about the hangar?

113
00:07:14,521 --> 00:07:15,898
Not really.

114
00:07:16,231 --> 00:07:19,860
Although, I left the hangar
five minutes before the bomb exploded.

115
00:07:20,110 --> 00:07:22,404
Did everything seem okay before that?

116
00:07:22,863 --> 00:07:24,949
Everything seemed normal.

117
00:07:26,075 --> 00:07:28,702
Is it true a Jedi might be
responsible for the attack?

118
00:07:30,537 --> 00:07:33,707
We're not certain of anything at this point.

119
00:07:37,044 --> 00:07:38,796
This distrust is troubling.

120
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:41,674
Some of these people
have worked in the Temple for years.

121
00:07:41,757 --> 00:07:46,011
Fear makes even the most
trusting individual irrational.

122
00:07:46,345 --> 00:07:48,806
I think I know who did it.

123
00:07:49,723 --> 00:07:51,058
Who blew up the hangar.

124
00:07:54,395 --> 00:07:55,521
Who?

125
00:07:55,646 --> 00:07:58,774
I believe it was Jackar Bowmani.

126
00:07:58,857 --> 00:08:01,944
Jackar Bowmani. Who is Jackar?

127
00:08:02,277 --> 00:08:04,530
One of the maintenance crew in the hangar.

128
00:08:04,613 --> 00:08:06,240
Why do you think it was him?

129
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:10,411
I passed him
as I was going on my shift change.

130
00:08:11,412 --> 00:08:15,290
He had been working all morning
in the section the blast came from.

131
00:08:15,374 --> 00:08:17,459
It was the last place I saw him.

132
00:08:17,543 --> 00:08:18,919
Is this him?

133
00:08:20,587 --> 00:08:21,630
Yes.

134
00:08:21,714 --> 00:08:25,092
I need to know,
have you seen him since the explosion?

135
00:08:25,259 --> 00:08:29,930
No. Truthfully, I didn't see much
of anything after the explosion.

136
00:08:31,348 --> 00:08:32,433
Thank you.

137
00:08:39,648 --> 00:08:42,818
Looks like we need to find
Jackar Bowmani, Russo.

138
00:08:50,951 --> 00:08:52,286
Did you find anything?

139
00:08:52,453 --> 00:08:56,290
No. But the rumor about it
being a Jedi is growing, Ahsoka.

140
00:08:56,415 --> 00:08:59,126
I can feel the anger and confusion
throughout the Jedi Temple.

141
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,211
Russo and I have a lead.

142
00:09:01,295 --> 00:09:04,381
We are looking for one of
the Temple workers, Jackar Bowmani.

143
00:09:04,465 --> 00:09:07,634
One of the witnesses saw him
in the area where the bomb exploded,

144
00:09:07,718 --> 00:09:08,969
right before it happened,

145
00:09:09,136 --> 00:09:11,472
and we have not been able to find him.

146
00:09:11,597 --> 00:09:12,806
Anywhere.

147
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:15,559
Come on, nobody just disappears.

148
00:09:15,642 --> 00:09:18,645
Unless it was well planned out.

149
00:09:18,729 --> 00:09:21,065
Well, it had to be well planned out
to get past Jedi.

150
00:09:21,148 --> 00:09:22,983
I'll talk to security.

151
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:29,406
No more clones! Stop the violence!

152
00:09:29,490 --> 00:09:32,993
End the war! Stop the violence!

153
00:09:33,118 --> 00:09:34,745
Stop the violence!

154
00:09:40,501 --> 00:09:41,585
No more clones!

155
00:09:41,668 --> 00:09:43,587
They're all family and friends?

156
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:45,881
Yes, looking for answers.

157
00:09:45,964 --> 00:09:47,674
So am I, Cin.

158
00:09:47,758 --> 00:09:50,552
This is the guy who might be
behind all of this.

159
00:09:50,636 --> 00:09:52,679
If you see him, alert me immediately.

160
00:09:55,682 --> 00:09:58,102
-That is Jackar.
-You know this man?

161
00:09:58,185 --> 00:09:59,937
He is my husband.

162
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:02,523
I've been trying to reach him
since I heard of an explosion.

163
00:10:02,606 --> 00:10:03,690
Where is he?

164
00:10:03,774 --> 00:10:05,526
I need you to come with me.

165
00:10:12,783 --> 00:10:14,868
You have no idea where Jackar is?

166
00:10:15,369 --> 00:10:16,453
No.

167
00:10:16,537 --> 00:10:19,623
You are a Jedi and you cannot find him?

168
00:10:19,706 --> 00:10:21,917
I understand your frustration.

169
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,294
Don't! Just find Jackar.

170
00:10:24,378 --> 00:10:28,507
Letta, do you think Jackar
could do something like this?

171
00:10:28,590 --> 00:10:29,675
Blow up the Temple?

172
00:10:29,758 --> 00:10:32,136
Do you have any idea
what someone has to go through

173
00:10:32,219 --> 00:10:34,346
to work in the Jedi Temple? Hmm?

174
00:10:34,721 --> 00:10:37,474
Jackar dedicated his life
to serving the Jedi.

175
00:10:37,558 --> 00:10:39,059
It had been his dream.

176
00:10:39,143 --> 00:10:42,437
Not just anyone can walk
into your precious Temple.

177
00:10:42,521 --> 00:10:44,565
He passed all the entry tests
that were needed.

178
00:10:44,648 --> 00:10:47,109
Okay. I had to ask.

179
00:10:47,192 --> 00:10:49,736
Unfortunately, everyone's a suspect.

180
00:10:49,820 --> 00:10:52,489
Jackar would never do anything like this.

181
00:10:52,573 --> 00:10:54,408
Please, find him.

182
00:11:26,607 --> 00:11:27,691
Hmm...

183
00:11:27,774 --> 00:11:31,195
Based on the trajectory of the debris,

184
00:11:31,278 --> 00:11:35,032
it seems the blast came from there.

185
00:11:35,115 --> 00:11:38,202
Why is there no bomb residue?

186
00:11:38,285 --> 00:11:41,205
So you think whoever did this
triggered a ship to explode?

187
00:11:41,288 --> 00:11:42,623
We think so.

188
00:11:42,706 --> 00:11:45,876
Russo's trying to use the shrapnel
to determine that now.

189
00:11:45,959 --> 00:11:48,712
The witness says he saw Jackar in the area.

190
00:11:48,795 --> 00:11:52,507
Maybe Jackar planned to do this
and just kept quiet?

191
00:11:52,591 --> 00:11:53,842
Hmm. Or?

192
00:11:53,926 --> 00:11:56,678
It actually was a Jedi.

193
00:11:59,431 --> 00:12:02,601
I found something, an anomaly.

194
00:12:04,436 --> 00:12:07,022
Something that should not be here.

195
00:12:15,364 --> 00:12:17,658
These pieces came from the blast origin.

196
00:12:18,617 --> 00:12:23,372
They are covered with microscopic droids
of a highly volatile nature.

197
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:25,415
Nano-droids.

198
00:12:25,916 --> 00:12:27,876
Yes, nano-droids.

199
00:12:31,004 --> 00:12:33,632
Great. Now we're chasing nano-droids.

200
00:12:34,633 --> 00:12:36,635
Russo, go through security footage,

201
00:12:36,718 --> 00:12:39,346
try to see if Jackar
went to other parts of the Temple.

202
00:12:39,429 --> 00:12:41,014
Ahsoka, let's go find out

203
00:12:41,098 --> 00:12:44,559
how Jackar got his hands
on these nano-droids.

204
00:12:51,525 --> 00:12:53,568
Bowmani's file, Master Jedi.

205
00:12:54,111 --> 00:12:56,154
He's a munitions expert.

206
00:12:56,238 --> 00:13:00,742
Jackar was the foreman over all of
the gunships, bombs and weapons.

207
00:13:00,909 --> 00:13:02,828
His specialty was nano-weaponry.

208
00:13:02,911 --> 00:13:04,997
We've got to find this guy.

209
00:13:09,918 --> 00:13:12,671
Isn't that going a little too fast
for you to make sense out of it?

210
00:13:12,754 --> 00:13:14,506
It is simple data.

211
00:13:14,589 --> 00:13:18,593
At this pace I am able to view
hundreds of hours of footage.

212
00:13:18,677 --> 00:13:19,761
Have you found Jackar?

213
00:13:21,346 --> 00:13:22,514
No.

214
00:13:22,848 --> 00:13:25,392
I'll gather some Jedi
and search the Temple.

215
00:13:25,475 --> 00:13:27,853
If he's still here,
he might be planning another attack.

216
00:13:27,936 --> 00:13:32,316
Instead of Jedi, I have droids
that can do the job much faster.

217
00:13:46,371 --> 00:13:48,790
So, you've found nothing so far?

218
00:13:48,874 --> 00:13:50,459
We have a clue we're following.

219
00:13:50,542 --> 00:13:52,377
But we still don't have answers.

220
00:13:55,964 --> 00:13:58,675
It is imperative that the truth
be found soon.

221
00:13:58,759 --> 00:14:00,886
There are whispers
that the Senate will have a meeting

222
00:14:00,969 --> 00:14:02,679
to decide whether the military police

223
00:14:02,763 --> 00:14:05,390
will need to become involved
in the investigation.

224
00:14:05,474 --> 00:14:06,933
They can't do that.

225
00:14:08,977 --> 00:14:10,937
Clones died in that explosion.

226
00:14:11,021 --> 00:14:12,564
Maintenance clones working
on the gunships,

227
00:14:12,647 --> 00:14:14,024
as well as civilians.

228
00:14:14,107 --> 00:14:16,860
The Senate tends to take notice
of these things,

229
00:14:16,985 --> 00:14:18,820
no matter where they happen.

230
00:14:21,698 --> 00:14:24,951
<i>Master Skywalker,
we have found Jackar.</i>

231
00:14:25,035 --> 00:14:27,746
Lock down all exits so he can't escape!

232
00:14:39,633 --> 00:14:40,675
Where is he?

233
00:14:40,801 --> 00:14:43,845
Well, part of him is here.

234
00:14:44,513 --> 00:14:47,224
I don't think now is a good time to joke.

235
00:14:48,642 --> 00:14:51,895
This is all that remains of Jackar.

236
00:14:51,978 --> 00:14:53,313
His hand?

237
00:14:53,397 --> 00:14:56,525
The rest of him exploded.

238
00:14:56,608 --> 00:14:58,402
Because he was so close to the bomb?

239
00:14:58,527 --> 00:15:01,029
Because he was the bomb.

240
00:15:02,948 --> 00:15:04,282
What's this?

241
00:15:04,366 --> 00:15:06,076
The connection we were looking for

242
00:15:06,159 --> 00:15:08,370
to the explosion in the hangar.

243
00:15:09,037 --> 00:15:10,455
The nano-droids!

244
00:15:10,539 --> 00:15:13,041
How did they get in his bloodstream?

245
00:15:13,125 --> 00:15:16,044
Oh, this just keeps
getting better and better.

246
00:15:16,128 --> 00:15:19,714
We're going to have to
search Jackar's home for evidence.

247
00:15:46,575 --> 00:15:48,160
This is not the nicest place.

248
00:15:48,243 --> 00:15:51,872
I would've thought
working for the Jedi paid better.

249
00:16:02,007 --> 00:16:04,259
Letta? Are you here?

250
00:16:04,926 --> 00:16:07,387
You search for the droids, but be careful.

251
00:16:07,471 --> 00:16:10,807
And remember, he was a munitions expert.

252
00:16:10,891 --> 00:16:13,768
I'd rather not set off
another explosion today.

253
00:16:13,852 --> 00:16:16,396
I'll see if he left a note.

254
00:17:04,361 --> 00:17:05,445
Letta?

255
00:17:30,845 --> 00:17:32,180
Master!

256
00:17:33,682 --> 00:17:36,560
The sensors are picking up
traces from the disposal.

257
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:40,188
The nano-droids were in the food.

258
00:17:40,438 --> 00:17:42,482
Well, I guess the question now is,

259
00:17:42,566 --> 00:17:46,027
did he eat them willingly,
or did someone feed them to him?

260
00:17:46,111 --> 00:17:48,154
What... What are you doing here?

261
00:17:48,238 --> 00:17:50,657
We've learned Jackar
was involved in the bombing.

262
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:52,033
That can't be true.

263
00:17:52,158 --> 00:17:55,537
See if she has any nano-droids
on her, Ahsoka.

264
00:17:58,164 --> 00:18:00,125
Uh, nano-droids?

265
00:18:02,168 --> 00:18:03,253
She's clean.

266
00:18:03,795 --> 00:18:06,089
What do you mean "nano-droids"?

267
00:18:06,172 --> 00:18:10,218
We believe someone set Jackar up
and made him the bomb.

268
00:18:12,846 --> 00:18:15,307
I don't understand.

269
00:18:15,390 --> 00:18:17,892
Letta, I want to bring you in
for more questioning.

270
00:18:18,476 --> 00:18:22,606
Maybe you can help us
make sense out of all of this.

271
00:18:23,023 --> 00:18:25,775
I'll answer any question I can.

272
00:18:44,669 --> 00:18:46,588
Letta, stop! Letta!

273
00:18:52,135 --> 00:18:53,261
Letta!

274
00:18:57,057 --> 00:18:59,684
-Take the high road !
-Right, Master!

275
00:19:32,425 --> 00:19:33,843
Letta, stop!

276
00:19:38,056 --> 00:19:39,391
Let me go!

277
00:19:39,474 --> 00:19:41,601
Running means you know more
than you're telling us.

278
00:19:41,685 --> 00:19:45,355
Jackar's dead, and now you're trying to
blame his murder on me.

279
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:48,358
Nobody ever said he was dead.

280
00:19:50,694 --> 00:19:54,364
But running proves you had
something to do with the bomb.

281
00:19:54,447 --> 00:19:56,533
You don't know what you're talking about.

282
00:19:57,033 --> 00:20:01,329
People blamed Jedi because of you.
People were killed because of you.

283
00:20:01,413 --> 00:20:03,415
You can't prove anything.

284
00:20:03,498 --> 00:20:06,918
Did you feed the nano-droids to Jackar!

285
00:20:07,001 --> 00:20:09,754
You will answer me. Now!

286
00:20:13,216 --> 00:20:15,927
I did feed the nano-droids to Jackar.

287
00:20:16,010 --> 00:20:18,930
You set up your own husband to die.

288
00:20:19,055 --> 00:20:22,058
You're dealing with things
you don't understand.

289
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:24,894
Where you're going,

290
00:20:24,978 --> 00:20:28,148
you'll have plenty of time
to explain everything.

291
00:20:31,359 --> 00:20:33,027
We're holding Letta in a cell
below the Temple

292
00:20:33,111 --> 00:20:35,321
to await further questioning.

293
00:20:35,405 --> 00:20:38,742
<i>I am pleased to report
there were no other nano-droids</i>

294
00:20:38,825 --> 00:20:41,035
<i>found in the sweep of the Temple.</i>

295
00:20:41,119 --> 00:20:43,580
<i>I am also pleased to report,</i>

296
00:20:43,663 --> 00:20:48,334
<i>based on the security footage,
Jackar Bowmani acted alone.</i>

297
00:20:49,002 --> 00:20:53,089
<i>Which means no Jedi was involved.</i>

298
00:20:53,214 --> 00:20:55,383
Thanks, Russo. Good job.

299
00:20:56,718 --> 00:20:59,679
Did this woman say
what her reasons were for attacking us?

300
00:20:59,763 --> 00:21:02,015
Not yet, but we're working on that.

301
00:21:02,140 --> 00:21:04,768
I think we can guess
her motives easily enough.

302
00:21:04,893 --> 00:21:09,189
Public opinion is swaying against the Jedi.
That is becoming clear.

303
00:21:11,608 --> 00:21:15,737
This war is becoming less and less popular
every day it persists.

304
00:21:19,282 --> 00:21:22,202
Master, I'm relieved
we solved this case, but...

305
00:21:22,285 --> 00:21:23,995
What if it had been a Jedi?

306
00:21:24,078 --> 00:21:28,291
Yes, I don't know how I would've felt
if a Jedi was really behind this.

307
00:21:29,292 --> 00:21:32,837
There are going to be Jedi
who disappoint us, Ahsoka.

308
00:21:32,962 --> 00:21:36,966
But as long as we know there are good Jedi
who fight for what's right,

309
00:21:37,091 --> 00:21:39,177
it makes it all worthwhile.

310
00:21:39,201 --> 00:21:44,201
http://hiqve.com/

